# (Optional) Absolute path to the Python virtual environment used to run the
# CDI and upload scripts. Defaults to ~/.myenv when unset. If the path does not
# exist, the system Python (python3) is used instead.
# NOTE: must be an absolute path — shell variables like $HOME are NOT expanded
# when loaded from .env. Uncomment and adjust to your server's venv:
